abstract: Christen Dale is charged with manslaughter in beating death of her 3-year-old nephew Ethan Ali in Brooklyn.
lead_paragraph: Christen Dale, 21, was arrested and charged with manslaughter in the killing of her nephew, Ethan Ali, whom she had been babysitting for at the apartment where they both lived.

headline.main: Aunt Charged in Beating Death of Brooklyn Boy, 3
headline.print_headline: Aunt Charged in Beating Death of Boy
